From: Axel Naumann <Axel.Naumann@cern.ch>
Date: Fri, 9 Dec 2022 09:31:38 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 36/65] Add "cplusplus20" as module requirement:

This needs to be upstreamed.
---
 clang/lib/Basic/Module.cpp | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/clang/lib/Basic/Module.cpp b/clang/lib/Basic/Module.cpp
index ef4e61924d0e..934ae9b949c3 100644
--- a/clang/lib/Basic/Module.cpp
+++ b/clang/lib/Basic/Module.cpp
@@ -109,6 +109,7 @@ static bool hasFeature(StringRef Feature, const LangOptions &LangOpts,
                         .Case("cplusplus11", LangOpts.CPlusPlus11)
                         .Case("cplusplus14", LangOpts.CPlusPlus14)
                         .Case("cplusplus17", LangOpts.CPlusPlus17)
+                        .Case("cplusplus20", LangOpts.CPlusPlus20)
                         .Case("c99", LangOpts.C99)
                         .Case("c11", LangOpts.C11)
                         .Case("c17", LangOpts.C17)
